com.oracle.coherence.cdi.CdiMapListenerManager
@ApplicationScoped public class CdiMapListenerManager extends AnnotatedMapListenerManager
Registers discovered CDI observer-based MapListeners when the cache is created, and unregisters them when it's destroyed.
